#网上找的窗口全屏函数
DestroyFunc FuncFullScreen
AddtoFunc FuncFullScreen
+ I Current (State 5) Fullscreen-Stop
+ I TestRc Current (Maximizable) Fullscreen-Start

DestroyFunc Fullscreen-Start
AddtoFunc Fullscreen-Start
+ I WindowStyle NoTitle, HandleWidth 0 ,FixedSize, FixedPosition
+ I Current (!Maximized) Maximize
+ I ResizeMaximize 100 100
+ I State 5 true

DestroyFunc Fullscreen-Stop
AddtoFunc Fullscreen-Stop
+ I DestroyWindowStyle
+ I Maximize
+ I State 5 false

#网上找的窗口置顶函数
DestroyFunc FuncOnTop
AddtoFunc FuncOnTop
+ I Current (State 6) OnTop-Stop
+ I TestRc (Match) break
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) OnTop-Start

DestroyFunc OnTop-Start
AddtoFunc OnTop-Start
+ I WindowStyle StaysOnTop
+ I State 6 true

DestroyFunc OnTop-Stop
AddtoFunc OnTop-Stop
+ I WindowStyle StaysPut
+ I State 6 false

#网上找的QuickTerminal
DestroyFunc QuickTerminal
AddToFunc QuickTerminal
+ I All (QuickTerminal, CurrentDesk) Iconify
+ I TestRc (Match) break
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) Exec xterm +samename -title QuickTerminal -xrm QuickTerminal -name QuickTerminal
+ I wait QuickTerminal
+ I All (QuickTerminal, CurrentDesk) Resize 750p 300p
+ I All (QuickTerminal, CurrentDesk) Move 308p 0p

